OL,5, Chefs working in elite kitchens face   
OL,6, "extreme suffering" to produce         
OL,7, award-winning food, a new study        
OL,8, suggests.                              
OL,10,FResearchers heard that Michelin Star   
OL,11,Fchefs are sterilising their wounds on  
OL,12,Fhot stoves and plunging their hands    
OL,13,Finto deep-fat fryers to prove          
OL,14,Fthemselves at work.                    
OL,16,FOne of them said going on shift felt   
OL,17,Flike "going to war".                   
OL,19,FHowever, the study also found that many
OL,20,Fchefs still see the pain as "a medal of
OL,21,Fhonour".                               
